%C A129862 Row sums of the absolute values are s(n) = 1, 3, 9, 21, 54, 141, 369, 966, 2529, 6621, 17334, ... (i.e., s(n) = 3*|A219233(n-1)| for n > 0). - _R. J. Mathar_, May 31 2014
