%F A129862 T(n, k) = coefficients of ( (2-x)*Lucas(2*n-2, i*sqrt(x)) ) with T(0, 0) = 1, T(1, 0) = 2 and T(1, 1) = -1. - _G. C. Greubel_, Jun 21 2021
